26 RS BR 1369
1 AN ACT relating to road projects and declaring an emergency.
2 Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of Kentucky:
3 Section 1. The projects authorized by the General Assembly in this Act
4 constitute the official 2026-2028 Biennial Highway Construction Plan.
5 Section 2. Whereas the funding for these projects is provided by the
6 Transportation Cabinet Budget Bill, which takes effect upon its passage and approval by
7 the Governor or upon its otherwise becoming a law, an emergency is declared to exist
8 and this Act takes effect upon its passage and approval by the Governor or upon its
9 otherwise becoming a law.
10 Section 3. The 2026-2028 biennial highway construction plan is as follows:
